{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"98152da7a7","title":"无锡市部分工人患浮肿病","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7c35390db5","index":0,"year":1960,"month":8,"day":29,"articleId":"98152da7a7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"06bbf56893","name":"新华社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33fe893056","type":"title","text":"无锡市部分工人患浮肿病","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"98152da7a7"},{"id":"42917ca5d3","type":"authors","text":"新华社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"98152da7a7"},{"id":"b225cb9353","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社南京讯　无锡市部分工厂发现少数工人患有浮肿病。据申新纺织厂、缫丝一厂、正德袜厂等一百一十一家工厂统计，发现有浮肿病患者二千四百七十一人，约占这些工厂职工的2%。患者以女工为多。据初步分析发病的原因是：有些工厂工时过长，过度疲劳；有些厂高温、潮湿、空气混浊；营养不良，特别是蛋白质之类的养份不足；有的工人原来患有其他疾病，体质弱，抵抗力差。该市已组织医务力量及时治疗。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"98152da7a7"},{"id":"80ed60966f","type":"paragraph","text":"来源： 1960年8月29日新华社《内部参考》。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"98152da7a7"}],"page":{"id":"b4d571abbc","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"98152da7a7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}